EmailTemplate.subject: Welcome to Palmetto! It's time to start selling solar.
EmailTemplate.textOnly:
Dear {!Opportunity.Contact_First_Name__c},
Congratulations! We're excited to welcome you as an Independent Palmetto Alchemist with Palmetto. This invitation is valid for 90 days. If you're ready to get started, simply sign the documents we send over, including your Master Services Agreement, Non-Disclosure Agreement, ACH Payment and W-4 form.
Please let me know if you any questions or if we can provide additional information. Welcome to Palmetto!
Sincerely,
Scott Enoch Palmetto Alchemist Account Manager (843) 996-4596
